      },
      "description": "Presentation on \"Assessing the Frequency and the Intensity of Marine Heatwaves in the Barents Sea\" delivered at the ObsSea4Clim - BioEcoOcean Clustering Event I, that took place on 11-12 March 2025 in Sopot, Poland. The presentation was delivered by Ajith Joseph Kochuparampil (NERCI), presenting work done in ObsSea4Clim project. This presentation was part of Session 3: \"Marine heatwaves (MHW) in space and time: understanding thermal anomalies at ecologically relevant scales\".&nbsp;",
